    "body": "I've just found your [announcement](http://ipython.readthedocs.io/en/stable/whatsnew/version5.html) on 5.x series:\n\n_IPython no longer uses readline configuration (~/.inputrc). We hope that the functionality you want (e.g. vi input mode) will be available by configuring IPython directly (see Terminal IPython options). If somethingâ€™s missing, please file an issue._\n"
