    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "For the confused ones like me, the solution is to edit the profile file. To create a profile file run `ipython profile create`. Then in `~/.ipython/profile_default/ipython_config.py` search for `editing_mode` and change to `vi`.\n\n```\n# Shortcut style to use at the prompt. 'vi' or 'emacs'.\nc.TerminalInteractiveShell.editing_mode = 'vi'\n```\n\nMore settings can be found [here](http://ipython.readthedocs.io/en/stable/config/options/terminal.html).\n"
  },
